{
  "stem": "14060.8",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So that it was literally like a sand pit where they were working it up from the bottom.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was useful from the point of view that one of the things which a lot of people got injured during the war generally is from the aerial pressure which punctures your ear drums from-- even if you were not hurt by shrapnel or something or a bomb, the air pressure could deafen you.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the-- anything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Or even a piece of metal could fall on you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So from their point of view, it was a relative safety.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But we were in the open elements.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I never forget, it was a sunny autumn day when-- in-- in-- in 1944, and my brother and I and my father were out there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we-- as I told you earlier, we got wise to the events of war, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we knew that bombing always takes place when the leading plane makes a circle, a wide circle, like a cloud-- you know, like the red arrows do when they do the exercises.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "A wide circle, and that is the bombing target.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we were walking down there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "There was no particular guards there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And once we were let down there, that was that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I look up, and I just had time to say to my father and my brother, I touch them, I said, look up!",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The bombs go-- the bombs are coming here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And in this second, I don't know what reason, just out of instinct, I pushed my father and my brother forward, and they fell into the sand.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I fell on top of them, because I was-- they were bigger than me.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
